31.913" end="00:32.079">in</span> <span begin="00:32.079" end="00:32.234">charge</span> <span begin="00:32.234" end="00:32.413">of</span> <span begin="00:32.413" end="00:32.549">a</span> <span begin="00:32.549" end="00:33.049">trading</span> <span begin="00:33.049" end="00:33.635">charter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">十四岁的时候 他们把一份贸易章程交给他负责</span></p><p begin="00:33.815" end="00:38.048" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:33.815" end="00:34.128">And</span> <span begin="00:34.128" end="00:34.580">every</span> <span begin="00:34.580" end="00:34.883">day</span> <span begin="00:34.883" end="00:35.092">while</span> <span begin="00:35.092" end="00:35.639">slaves</span> <span begin="00:35.639" end="00:35.811">were</span> <span begin="00:35.811" end="00:36.186">being</span> <span begin="00:36.186" end="00:36.757">slaughtered</span> <span begin="00:36.757" end="00:36.972">and</span> <span begin="00:36.972" end="00:37.448">carted</span> <span begin="00:37.448" end="00:38.048">away</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">日日都有奴隶惨死 被运往他处</span></p><p begin="00:38.055" end="00:41.273" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:38.055" end="00:38.618">Across</span> <span begin="00:38.618" end="00:38.844">the</span> <span begin="00:38.844" end="00:39.308">waves,</span> <span begin="00:39.308" end="00:39.427">he</span> <span begin="00:39.427" end="00:40.046">struggled</span> <span begin="00:40.046" end="00:40.147">and</span> <span begin="00:40.147" end="00:40.289">kept</span> <span begin="00:40.289" end="00:40.516">his</span> <span begin="00:40.516" end="00:40.813">guard</span> <span begin="00:40.813" end="00:41.273">up</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">穿越汹涌波涛 他挣扎求生 小心谨慎</span></p><p begin="00:41.288" end="00:44.843" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:41.288" end="00:42.059">Inside,</span> <span begin="00:42.059" end="00:42.255">he</span> <span begin="00:42.255" end="00:42.499">was</span> <span be