 begin="00:54.221" end="00:54.655">drip,</span> <span begin="00:54.655" end="00:55.138">dripping</span> <span begin="00:55.138" end="00:55.389">down</span> <span begin="00:55.389" end="00:55.621">the</span> <span begin="00:55.621" end="00:56.135">drain</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们的主人公眼睁睁看着前途一点一点被冲毁</span></p><p begin="00:56.375" end="01:00.008" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="00:56.375" end="00:56.475">Put</span> <span begin="00:56.475" end="00:56.575">a</span> <span begin="00:56.575" end="00:56.997">pencil</span> <span begin="00:56.997" end="00:57.259">to</span> <span begin="00:57.259" end="00:57.485">his</span> <span begin="00:57.485" end="00:57.979">temple,</span> <span begin="00:57.979" end="00:58.717">connected</span> <span begin="00:58.717" end="00:58.949">it</span> <span begin="00:58.949" end="00:59.192">to</span> <span begin="00:59.192" end="00:59.436">his</span> <span begin="00:59.436" end="01:00.008">brain</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">铅笔抵在太阳穴 连接起头脑中的思想</span></p><p begin="01:00.020" end="01:03.636" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:00.020" end="01:00.236">And</span> <span begin="01:00.236" end="01:00.402">he</span> <span begin="01:00.402" end="01:00.620">wrote</span> <span begin="01:00.620" end="01:00.820">his</span> <span begin="01:00.820" end="01:01.119">first</span> <span begin="01:01.119" end="01:01.719">refrain,</span> <span begin="01:01.719" end="01:01.938">a</span> <span begin="01:01.938" end="01:02.620">testament</span> <span begin="01:02.620" end="01:02.887">to</span> <span begin="01:02.887" end="01:03.138">his</span> <span begin="01:03.138" end="01:03.636">pain</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">他写下人生第一篇文章 剖白自己的苦痛</span></p><p begin="01:03.646" end="01:07.764" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:03.646" end="01:03.803">Well,</span> <span begin="01:03.803" end="01:04.086">the</span> <span begin="01:04.086" end="01:04.555">word</span> <spa